    "body": "Working around this in my app by delegating the message to all `<webview>`s. Perhaps an internal fix would look similar.\n\n``` coffee\n{remote} = require(\"electron\")\n\ndocument.addEventListener \"visibilitychange\", ->\n  hostWindow = remote.getCurrentWindow()\n  isVisible = hostWindow.isVisible()\n  isMinimized = hostWindow.isMinimized()\n\n  for webview in document.querySelectorAll(\"webview\")\n    webview.getWebContents().send(\"ATOM_RENDERER_WINDOW_VISIBILITY_CHANGE\", isVisible, isMinimized)\n```\n"
  },
